@startuml
' Diagram: F07 - Ghi nhan phi duy tri va lich su hoa don POI (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 0121e4f
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/GhiNhan.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), OnPostAsync(), LoadPoiAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/LichSu.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync()
' Note: Sequence mo ta luong Razor PageModel o cap method + persistence, khong liet ke cau SQL.
' Note: Luong gom moc gia han, upsert DangKyDichVu, va tao HoaDon theo tung thang; khong suy dien them PaymentController du phong.
title F07 - Ghi nhan phi duy tri va lich su hoa don POI

actor Admin
control "ThanhToan/IndexModel" as IndexModel
control "GhiNhanModel" as GhiNhanModel
control "LichSuModel" as LichSuModel
participant "AppDbContext\n<<persistence>>" as DbContext
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> IndexModel: OnGetAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: POIs.Include(DangKyDichVus).Include(HoaDons).ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read POI payment rows
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: data
IndexModel --> Admin: render list + summary

Admin -> GhiNhanModel: OnGetAsync(poiId)
GhiNhanModel -> DbContext: LoadPoiAsync(poiId)
DbContext -> DB: read POI package and recent invoices
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> GhiNhanModel: data
GhiNhanModel --> Admin: render form

Admin -> GhiNhanModel: OnPostAsync()
GhiNhanModel -> DbContext: LoadPoiAsync(poiId)
DbContext -> DB: read current maintenance state
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> GhiNhanModel: poi + goi
note right of GhiNhanModel
  OnPostAsync() computes renewal anchor,
  updates POI, upserts DangKyDichVu,
  and creates HoaDon rows by month.
end note
GhiNhanModel -> DbContext: SaveChangesAsync()
DbContext -> DB: persist maintenance changes
DB --> DbContext: saved
GhiNhanModel --> Admin: Redirect /ThanhToan

opt open invoice history
  Admin -> LichSuModel: OnGetAsync(poiId)
  LichSuModel -> DbContext: HoaDons.Where(...).OrderByDescending(...).ToListAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read invoice history rows
  DB --> DbContext: HoaDon rows
  DbContext --> LichSuModel: hoa don
  LichSuModel --> Admin: render history table
end
@enduml
